lyrics:

[Intro: Melody, Paula Guilherme]
Melody
Isso é Paula Guilherme

Meu bonde usa chapéu, fivela e bota, bota, bota
O rodeio para quando eu faço o movimento de galopa
Galopa, galopa

imageDescription: A simple image that best represents the song is a Barbie doll wearing a cowboy hat and boots, standing confidently in a field with a lasso in hand. The image captures the idea of a "princess of the rodeo" with a playful and mischievous vibe.
